      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Twelve self-contained modules, simple to navigate but detailed once you're in one — read left to right, top to bottom.\nEach has a plain-English hook up top and the real mechanics (package names, protocol frames, real numbers) below it.",
