    {
      "id": "txt_27",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1184,
      "y": 404,
      "width": 902,
      "height": 612,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#212529",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame_13",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1053,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1054,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "cmd/junto/main.go\n  |- junto create <files|url>   -> app.Create()\n  |- junto join <code> [files]  -> app.Join()\n  `- both converge on runSession() -> syncer.Engine.Run()\n\nrunSession() is the composition root — it wires:\n  * mpv.Launch()      spawns mpv, connects its JSON IPC socket\n  * nostrx.Transport  signs + encrypts + sends/receives relay events\n  * syncer.Deps{}     the dependency-injection struct: Mpv client, a Send\n                      func, the relay inbox channel, OnFileReq/OnSignal\n                      hooks, Buffer + DownloadProgress channels\n\nHOST only:      also spawns transfer.ServeFile() per joiner request\nJOINER, streaming (no local files): also spawns transfer.Downloader\n                      + streamserver.Server\n\ncheckMpvEarly() runs BEFORE any relay work — a missing mpv fails in\nunder a second instead of after a ~10s relay connect attempt",
      "fontSize": 12.5,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rect_26",
      "originalText": "cmd/junto/main.go\n  |- junto create <files|url>   -> app.Create()\n  |- junto join <code> [files]  -> app.Join()\n  `- both converge on runSession() -> syncer.Engine.Run()\n\nrunSession() is the composition root — it wires:\n  * mpv.Launch()      spawns mpv, connects its JSON IPC socket\n  * nostrx.Transport  signs + encrypts + sends/receives relay events\n  * syncer.Deps{}     the dependency-injection struct: Mpv client, a Send\n                      func, the relay inbox channel, OnFileReq/OnSignal\n                      hooks, Buffer + DownloadProgress channels\n\nHOST only:      also spawns transfer.ServeFile() per joiner request\nJOINER, streaming (no local files): also spawns transfer.Downloader\n                      + streamserver.Server\n\ncheckMpvEarly() runs BEFORE any relay work — a missing mpv fails in\nunder a second instead of after a ~10s relay connect attempt",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "baseline": 12.5
    },
