      "versionNonce": 1164,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"at\" + 16 KiB binary chunks + \"eof\"",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"at\" + 16 KiB binary chunks + \"eof\"",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "rect_83",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 2260,
      "y": 1370,
      "width": 930,
      "height": 640,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame_73",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 1165,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1166,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "txt_84"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "txt_84",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2274,
      "y": 1384,
      "width": 902,
      "height": 612,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#212529",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame_73",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1167,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1168,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "control frames (JSON text) share the data channel with binary chunks:\n  joiner -> host:  {\"t\":\"start\",\"seq\":S,\"off\":N,\"len\":L}\n                   {\"t\":\"done\"}\n  host -> joiner:  {\"t\":\"at\",\"seq\":S,\"off\":N}\n                   {\"t\":\"eof\",\"seq\":S}\n                   {\"t\":\"err\",\"msg\":M}\n\n* backpressure: sender pauses once 8 MiB is queued-but-unsent\n* adaptive window: downloader keeps 32-512 MB ahead of the playhead,\n  sized to ~30s of headroom at the measured throughput\n* a seek REDIRECTS the same connection instead of reconnecting\n* a stall watchdog fails the transfer (resumable) if zero new bytes\n  arrive for 30s, even though the connection still looks alive\n* resume: .part file + .part.junto sidecar (received byte spans) —\n  quitting mid-download and rejoining resumes instead of restarting\n* every completed file is SHA-256 verified against the announced hash",
      "fontSize": 12.5,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "rect_83",
      "originalText": "control frames (JSON text) share the data channel with binary chunks:\n  joiner -> host:  {\"t\":\"start\",\"seq\":S,\"off\":N,\"len\":L}\n                   {\"t\":\"done\"}\n  host -> joiner:  {\"t\":\"at\",\"seq\":S,\"off\":N}\n                   {\"t\":\"eof\",\"seq\":S}\n                   {\"t\":\"err\",\"msg\":M}\n\n* backpressure: sender pauses once 8 MiB is queued-but-unsent\n* adaptive window: downloader keeps 32-512 MB ahead of the playhead,\n  sized to ~30s of headroom at the measured throughput\n* a seek REDIRECTS the same connection instead of reconnecting\n* a stall watchdog fails the transfer (resumable) if zero new bytes\n  arrive for 30s, even though the connection still looks alive\n* resume: .part file + .part.junto sidecar (received byte spans) —\n  quitting mid-download and rejoining resumes instead of restarting\n* every completed file is SHA-256 verified against the announced hash",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "baseline": 12.5
    },
    {
